Your personalized SwiftKey Account is the first step towards a better typing experience. We can't wait to show you how to make the most of it.

Personalize- Connect your social accounts to teach SwiftKey more about how you type for even better predictions.
Backup & Sync - Lost your phone or got a new tablet? No problem: your SwiftKey Account backs up your personalized predictions, so you'll be back up and running in no time.
SwiftKey Store - Check out over 100 themes to customize your keyboard.
Find your perfect layout - Tap the three dashes on the top left of your keyboard to access the SwiftKey Hub with quick-change layout options, easy theme switching, and personalized stats.
SwiftKey Support Want to learn about how to make the most of all the SwiftKey settings and options? Check out our new user guides. You can also always get to more FAQs and articles, or contact the SwiftKey Community team in our Support Portal.

